        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Poor thing!\" said the old poet, as he went to open the door.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Poor child!\" said the old poet, as he took the boy by the hand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Thou shalt have wine and roasted apples, for thou art verily a charming child!\" And the boy was so really.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "His eyes were like two bright stars; and although the water trickled down his hair, it waved in beautiful curls.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "He looked exactly like a little angel, but he was so pale, and his whole body trembled with cold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"You are a merry fellow,\" said the old man.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"What's your name?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"My name is Cupid,\" answered the boy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Don't you know me?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000014_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000014_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Look, the weather is now clearing up, and the moon is shining clear again through the window.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "The poor poet lay on the earth and wept, for the arrow had really flown into his heart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "I will tell all children about him, that they may take care and not play with him, for he will only cause them sorrow and many a heartache.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "And all good children to whom he related this story, took great heed of this naughty Cupid; but he made fools of them still, for he is astonishingly cunning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Yes, he is forever following people.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Ask them only and you will hear what they'll tell you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "He is forever running after everybody.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Only think, he shot an arrow once at your old grandmother!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122809_000020_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122809/439_122809_000020_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "But that is a long time ago, and it is all past now; however, a thing of that sort she never forgets.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Now Karen was old enough to be confirmed; she had new clothes and was to have new shoes also.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "All this looked charming, but the old lady could not see well, and so had no pleasure in them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "In the midst of the shoes stood a pair of red ones, just like those the princess had worn.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "The next Sunday there was the sacrament, and Karen looked at the black shoes, looked at the red ones-looked at them again, and put on the red shoes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "The sun shone gloriously; Karen and the old lady walked along the path through the corn; it was rather dusty there.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Sit firm when you dance\"; and he put his hand out towards the soles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "And Karen could not help dancing a step or two, and when she began her feet continued to dance; it was just as though the shoes had power over them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "The shoes were placed in a closet at home, but Karen could not avoid looking at them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "She danced, and was forced to dance straight out into the gloomy wood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Dance shalt thou!\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Dance shalt thou-!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Mercy!\" cried Karen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Here, she knew, dwelt the executioner; and she tapped with her fingers at the window, and said, \"Come out!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "Come out!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000031_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000031_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "I cannot come in, for I am forced to dance!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Don't strike my head off!\" said Karen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "\"Then I can't repent of my sins! But strike off my feet in the red shoes!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "And the clergyman's wife was sorry for her and took her into service; and she was industrious and thoughtful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "And he touched the ceiling with the spray, and the ceiling rose so high, and where he had touched it there gleamed a golden star.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_122810_000040_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/122810/439_122810_000040_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "For the church itself had come to the poor girl in her narrow chamber, or else she had come into the church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-439_123866_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/439/123866/439_123866_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-439",
        "content": "twenty two.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
